&lt;p&gt;If you are looking for something non-wiki-based take a look at &lt;a href="http://plone.org"&gt;Plone&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="http://alfresco.com/"&gt;Alfresco&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
